name: GPU Ordinals by Anarkoic
description: GPU Ordinals by Anarkoic is the first ever WebGPU Ordinals collection. WebGPU is the new technology that provides high-throughput use of GPU's for graphics and even computation, & can enable high-performance Metaverses and LLM AI's on Bitcoin. This immersive, interactive 3D collection also features Grandparent-Grandchild Inscription, Spatial Audio, Real-time Block Streaming & introduces Super-Recursion. Max Supply 2100.
